textBeforeTable: Basic Subscription: Subscribers have access to only Active ASTM standards documents. Plus Subscription: Subscribers have access to all ASTM standards documents available, including Active, Redline, Historical and Withdrawn standards. Subscription Period: The subscription ends 12 months from the day your order is processed. It also provides standards on gaskets used in transportation applications, as well as standards related to commercial nonmetallic gaskets, enveloped gaskets, and laminate composite gasket materials (LCGM) for use with corrosion-resistant process equipment. Volume 09.02 features specifications, tests, and practices for evaluating rubber surgical and examination gloves; automotive and aeronautical rubber; packing, seals, and gasket materials; hose and belting; coated fabrics; latex foam, sponge, expanded cellular rubber, and tires. The 80+ volume Annual Book of ASTM Standards contains ASTM's 12,000+ standards and is available in print, CD-ROM and Online formats (learn more about format options). The volumes can be purchased individually, as a section (at a 25% discount) or as the complete 80+ volume set (at a 50% discount).
